<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>  
        <title>Login</title>
    </head>
    <body style="background-image: url('../index_images/29000056.jpg'); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: cover;">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <header style="width: 50%;">
                <div>
                    <div class="font-weight-bold" style="font-size: 35px; color: white;">
                        <p>Matcha</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </header>
            <form action="/verify" method="post" style="margin-left: 10%;">
                    <div class="row">
                        <fieldset style="border: 1px solid white; border-radius: 10px;">
                            <legend style="width: auto; color: white; position: relative; top: -3px;">Login</legend>
                                <div class="col-sm-6" style="margin-top: 150px;">
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="username" placeholder="Username" style="width: 270px; height: 30px;">
                                    <br />
                                    <br />
                                    <input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" placeholder="Password" style="width: 270px; height: 30px;">
                                    <br />
                                    <br />
                                    <input class="btn btn-outline-light text-light btn-sm" type="submit" name="submit" value="Login" style="width: 270px; height: 30px;">
                                    <p style="margin-left: 125px; color: white" class="font-weight-light">OR</p>
                                    <a  class="btn btn-outline-light text-light btn-sm" style="margin-top: -14px; width: 270px; height: 30px;" href="/signup">Signup</a>
                                    <p style="margin-left: 125px; color: white" class="font-weight-light">OR</p>
                                    <a  class="btn btn-outline-light text-light btn-sm" style="margin-top: -14px; margin-bottom: 44px; width: 270px; height: 30px;" href="/forgot_password">Forgot password ?</a>
                                </div>
                        </fieldset>
                        <div class="col-sm-6" style="margin-top: 150px;">
                            <p class="font-weight-light" style="color: white; ">
                                Mature love says 'I need you because I love you.'” “Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength, while loving someone deeply gives you courage.” “One word frees us of all the weight and pain of life: That word is love.” “The deeper that sorrow carves into your being, the more joy you can contain
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
            </form>
            <%
                if (info == "token has been verified")
                {
            %>
            <script>
                alert("Your account has been successfully verified, you may log in now");
            </script>
            <%
                }
                else if (verified == "false")
                {
            %>
            <script>
                alert("You need to verify your account inorder to login.");
            </script>
            <%
                }
                else if (login == "details does not exist")
                {
            %>
            <script>
                alert("The details you provided does not exist.");
            </script>
            <%
                }
                else if (login == "incorrect details")
                {
            %>
                <script>
                    alert("Incorrect Username or Password.");
                </script>
            <%
                }
            %>
        </div>
        <footer>© 2020 matcha project</footer>
    </body>
</html> 